Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 08:32:09 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Implement polymorphic types

This is a very literal implementation of system F's typing rules: We've added a type former, constructor and eliminator for forall types and directly adapted the existing abstraction inference code for them
